{
  "stem": "27390.8",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And to this day, I have never gone back to Poland.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And after I managed to recover a bit, we were given permission by the Russian commandant that was in charge of the ghetto to bring in German prisoners to do- to clean up the place.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We gave them back a bit of the medicine that they gave us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And it's amazing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We were skeletons.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And, we- and I could go up to a higher ranking officer.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "He was 6 foot tall.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And if he would have given one blow with his mouth, I would have fallen down.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I wasonly- I was very weak.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And he was terrified of me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And whatever I asked him to do, he did.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It felt very good.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I must say, it felt very good.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But some people they had it in them the first three days, the Russians allowed to do what we like with the Germans.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I didn't- I-I didn't first of all, I didn't have the strength-- it's not so easy to kill somebody.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Some people, there was a river there, the Vltava, and the river was mined.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Germans mined it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because they didn't want the Russians to cross over.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And some people got hold of, especially SS, if they knew they SS men, they got hold of them, and they threw them into the river, and that was [INAUDIBLE] certain death.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because as soon as they fell down, they exploded.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The mines killed them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But what we did do with the Germans, we brought them into work.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And in the evening, we took them back to the-- there was a POW-- a prisoner of war camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, it's got to be now.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All right.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
